title: The Amazing Kaylee and the Tricky Mr. Fox
description: Welcome to the final book in the Amazing Kaylee series. We join Kaylee and her friends back on the farm just in time for the holidays! We find that someone is up to their old tricks again, but maybe he's just looking for some friends? Kaylee and the farm crew are having a great time solving the riddles and discover a soft side of the prankster, Mr. Fox.
author: Daniel Dean Morris II
